head-on accident...

271
00:16:20,585 --> 00:16:23,985
LAUGHTER

272
00:16:23,985 --> 00:16:27,145
You could never have a
head-on crash.

273
00:16:27,145 --> 00:16:30,625
This is one of these windy-up cars,
