00:18:07,305 --> 00:18:09,065
As Jeremy pointed out last series,

308
00:18:09,065 --> 00:18:11,385
Boris has been rather
faffing about on this one.

309
00:18:11,385 --> 00:18:14,945
So we figured it was about time
for some Top Gear help.

310
00:18:14,945 --> 00:18:17,545
Whether he wanted it or not.

311
00:18:19,185 --> 00:18:22,985
