the Monza of southern England.

325
00:19:07,585 --> 00:19:10,265
By people who've
never been to Monza.

326
00:19:10,265 --> 00:19:13,865
It's normally a rallycross circuit,
so it is a challenging mix

327
00:19:13,865 --> 00:19:18,505
