340
00:20:03,345 --> 00:20:06,625
Now, because there is so much
at stake here,

341
00:20:06,625 --> 00:20:10,225
we can't leave the driving
to any old bus driver.

342
00:20:10,225 --> 00:20:13,625
So we brought in our old friends,
