legend, Anthony Reid.

346
00:20:27,105 --> 00:20:30,585
Touring car legend, Matt Neal.

347
00:20:34,665 --> 00:20:39,985
And, for the second time tonight,
hairdressing legend, Tom Chilton.

348
00:20:41,865 --> 00:20:45,185
To be honest, they're not that good
